data.description: H11264 - Located in the center of beautiful Bonita Springs this spacious home with 1970 square feet and four bedrooms offers the opportunity to live the laid-back Florida lifestyle. Villages of Bonita is within walking distance to active Downtown Bonita and Riverside Park, the location couldn't be better.   SWFL INTL Airport is 25 minutes away and the Bonita Beaches are a short 6 miles away. Kitchen overlooks a nice back yard and has an eat-in dining area. Home has a large living/dining area. Master bedroom has two walk-in closets, bath has separate tub and shower plus dual vanities. Second bath also has dual vanities. Roof and A/C were replaced in 2020 and there is an oversized two-car garage as well as a screened lanai and an outdoor patio. All rooms are generous sizes. Amenities are just a short walk away and include a community pool, community room, spa, tennis and shuffleboard. You will enjoy living in this charming gated community with low HOA fees. Come and enjoy this spacious bright home!
